Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.32,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.71,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Under the rader I'm reaching for the sky
