Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.98,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光を灯す為 今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.30,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊すFate & Fear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:13.91,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生まれ持った衝動で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:20.30,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}全てを掴み獲れ今すぐ ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.04,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}真実を手に!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:51.37,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}扣下击断烦恼的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:55.77,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毫无用处的自尊在垃圾回收日舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:02:00.77,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}猎取一切的武士疯狂起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.50,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:06.86,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:11.02,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:15.72,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在叹息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:19.60,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟随神风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.14,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向着未知之处前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.14,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的热情与
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:32.34,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}熏染的灵魂勒紧胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.80,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃烧的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.32,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.71,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:49.17,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:57.74,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}纵情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:04.95,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}继续这不羁的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:17.53,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃焦这唯一的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.73,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}前进直到血干枯之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:32.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}远方天空反射过来的光照耀此身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.67,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}消逝散落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:42.35,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}胸中充满激烈的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:56.25,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}紧握的手的疼痛谁人能知!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.06,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毁灭破坏与和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:02.58,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}悄无声息迫近的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.98,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}只为点亮光明  现在正是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.30,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毁灭破坏与和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:13.91,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}用与生俱来的冲动
